subtitleNullable: Image Data of peoples with mask during this COVID19 pandemic.
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset can be used for mask recognition system based on facial recognition system during this COVID19 pandemic.

### Content

In this data set we are having two data set: test & train having VOC PASCAL XML & YOLO annotations.

### Acknowledgements

This dataset's annotations as build over the data set provided [here](https://www.kaggle.com/andrewmvd/face-mask-detection).

### Inspiration

While I am working with Face Mask Detection system with YOLO, majorly data set are coming with VOC PASCAL annotation instead of YOLO annotation. To serve this YOLO annotation need I had added these YOLO annotations to the data set also.
